  EntityId: boss.security_boss
  DisplayName: Security Boss
  Description: He has spent centuries reviewing casino security protocols. Every
    action is recorded in his incident book. He detected thousands of cheaters in
    his lifetime and continues applying the same procedures even if there is no one
    left alive to protect. If the player repeats a move, he already has it recorded.
  WeaknessComboId: 
  WeaknessMultiplierOverride: 0
  BaseHP: 20
  BaseAttack: 0
  BaseHealStrength: 5
  BaseSpeed: 4
  MaxEnergy: 3
  BaseAttackRange: 1
